trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> que tem como destino o método <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty,System.Object)" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Object" /> to set the value to.

Allows a custom override of the <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty,System.Object)" /> logic associated with a dependency property that is defined on a dependency object.
trans-unit.target: Permite uma substituição personalizada da lógica <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty,System.Object)" /> associada a uma propriedade de dependência definida em um objeto de dependência.

trans-unit.source: The implementation of this delegate can be set to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.SetValueOverride%2A> property of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> while calling <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.
trans-unit.target: A implementação deste delegado pode ser definida como o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.SetValueOverride%2A> propriedade <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> ao chamar <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> ou <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.
